data.description: Welcome to this Ranch-style home with numerous desirable features, including impact windows and doors, and a real fireplace... House sits on an oversized lot, providing ample space for outdoor activities and potential expansion. Enjoy sunny Florida days by the large pool or retreat to the cozy Florida room for year-round relaxation. The property features office space for a convenient work-from-home setup. The roof has been recently repaired and inspected for long-lasting durability, and a new central AC system ensures optimal comfort. A circular driveway adds elegance and ample parking. Located minutes from Broward Mall, Plantation Walk, and parks, it offers the perfect blend of convenience and tranquility. Don't miss out on the chance to renovate this house and make it your own paradise!
